{"tid":1462251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔屌前線手足，但忍唔住要屌你班善忘嘅香港人","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:33:55.000Z","uid":72209,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"4a4370b4c6745ead3bb3290c802c8e14df46cf60","tid":1462251,"uid":72209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:14:18.000Z","msg":"今日無乜人嚟，所以要癱瘓機場運作只可以靠僅有嘅人手直接阻住旅客出境。大家先唔好屌咁樣做唔做得啱，我都覺得直接阻旅客係弊多於利，但我最想屌嘅，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係點解大家可以咁撚善忘</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n尋日可以咁多人，8.11一定有加成，我地香港人都因為8.11嘅義士，特別爆眼女義士而好撚嬲，所以先可以咁疊馬塞爆機場。但<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">過咗一日咋，大家去哂邊呀？</span></strong>如果今日多人，塞埋佢交通，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">班手足使唔使做到咁肉酸起人鏈呀？</span></strong>而家香港係處於<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">國家存亡之秋</span></strong>，香港人，唔好咁善忘，比番團火出嚟好冇？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日再去機場，做番我地手足，一齊逼爆佢好冇？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n香港人，毋忘721、811。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6e00b17a57fe156c1738d977803d89516aaacf2a","tid":1462251,"uid":43751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:15:01.000Z","msg":"無撚講錯"},{"pid":"1f66f72953c07fc95a67940eddea018fd6db8426","tid":1462251,"uid":173279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:15:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>機場旅客好撚燥 你可以點做？</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1462138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1462138</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><em>幫旅客/教旅客聯絡領事館同旅發局！！！</em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n推啊！！！！<br />\n大家唔好乜都攬上身，<br />\n交返個波比柒婆呀！！！"},{"pid":"25734a3ce3882045c2fc358d592c1a21fdc38539","tid":1462251,"uid":47801,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:15:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b94e256